57
00:04:30,351 --> 00:04:32,338
<i>Almost none. He
seems stabilized.</i>

58
00:04:32,405 --> 00:04:36,240
- Dr. House, is there
anything back from micro?
- Not yet. You gonna fire me?

59
00:04:36,309 --> 00:04:39,871
