by washing my car.
- Oh, this is fun.

60
00:04:39,946 --> 00:04:42,347
<i>Okay. Let's keep him on the
broad-spectrum antibiotics.</i>

61
00:04:42,415 --> 00:04:44,680
And since he's displaying
septic physiology,

