try putting the guy on I.V.I.G.?

78
00:05:36,937 --> 00:05:40,339
- No, because the M.R.I. showed
no— - Well, let's do an M.R.I. of our own.

79
00:05:43,844 --> 00:05:46,313
Guys, it's my case.

80
00:05:47,981 --> 00:05:52,419
<i>A. L.S. fits. It even predicts the
pneumonia. The paralysis is progressive.</i>

81
00:05:52,485 --> 00:05:56,786
It's a death sentence.
