It makes sense.

86
00:06:22,282 --> 00:06:24,274
So it's just gonna
get worse, huh?

87
00:06:24,351 --> 00:06:26,286
- Well, Dr. Hamilton—
- Great guy.

88
00:06:26,353 --> 00:06:30,017
Really smart doctor, and his
treatment obviously isn't working.

89
00:06:32,225 --> 00:06:35,992
