aren't making him sad.
- Oh, my God. You don't believe that.

183
00:12:56,109 --> 00:12:59,910
- His thyroid levels were a little—
- It's nothing. Do not defend him!

184
00:12:59,979 --> 00:13:02,710
- Why did he sign that D.N.R.?
- I-I didn't talk him into...

185
00:13:02,782 --> 00:13:07,049
No. He signed the D.N.R. 'cause he didn't
want a slow, painful death from A.L.S.

186
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:10,579
