330
00:21:56,081 --> 00:21:58,209
I have the right to face
my accuser. Judge said so.

331
00:21:58,284 --> 00:22:02,517
Not if no one's accusing you. All
the charges have been dropped.

332
00:22:09,195 --> 00:22:11,221
He doesn't have to die.

333
00:22:14,099 --> 00:22:16,034
It's not Wegener's.

334
00:22:31,016 --> 00:22:34,180
If it's Wegener's, his lungs
