344
00:24:14,620 --> 00:24:16,885
Do you think he's
just being stubborn?

345
00:24:16,956 --> 00:24:19,619
He's alive because you were
wrong. It's not Wegener's.

346
00:24:19,692 --> 00:24:23,754
